jparsec.ephem

Class Target

  • java.lang.Object
    • jparsec.ephem.Target

  • public final class Target
extends java.lang.Object
    A common place to store target body IDs. This class is updated following new IAU resolutions about Pluto.

    Size parameters comes from the IAU2009 recommended values. Note that not all known natural objects are listed here, but only those whose size or rotational parameters are known. Otherwise, ephemeris can also be obtained for objects not listed here (see MoonEphem.calcAllJPLSatellites(jparsec.time.TimeElement, jparsec.observer.ObserverElement, EphemerisElement)).

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    T. Alonso Albi - OAN (Spain)
